title: Presidio of San Francisco: People
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     History & Culture     People               People        Historic figures at the Presidio from left to right: Frederick Funston, Concepcion Arguello, Charles Young, John J. Pershing and Dana Crissy with family.       Through the centuries, many famous and interesting personalities left their mark on the Presidio and our country. Use the links below to view brief biographical sketches of some of the individuals with lasting legacies at the Presidio.
